          name: "Learning Objectives",
          desc: "Students will have achieved the proficiency in German necessary to advance to German 102-1. They will be able to converse on basic topics and have the reading skills necessary to understand authentic texts and will also be able to write informative texts with demonstrated control of basic grammatical forms.",
